    "updated_at": "2023-07-31T15:01:41Z",
    "body": "For people looking for a quick workaround on **macOS**, this worked for me:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nwget 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/homebrew-core/b29a0f0b835e035b75cf349a9622e6aa4959bff0/Formula/starship.rb' && \r\nbrew remove starship && brew install starship.rb\r\n```\r\n\r\nWill downgrade to version 1.15.0.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
