    "body": "Meet the same problem today, and the following solution works.\r\n\r\n> Workround that work on me for Mac Mini.\r\n> \r\n> ```\r\n> $ startship config\r\n> ```\r\n> \r\n> add this lines\r\n> \r\n> ```\r\n> [battery]\r\n> disabled = true\r\n> ```\r\n\r\n",
